46
00:02:20,944 --> 00:02:22,707
Bola uškrtená.

47
00:02:22,707 --> 00:02:24,011
Sme presvedčení,

48
00:02:24,256 --> 00:02:26,686
že ju uškrtil Jo Ho Young.

49
00:02:28,803 --> 00:02:30,417
Nie.

50
00:02:30,772 --> 00:02:33,075
